description:
I made this app to create an accumulation of the presentations done at the webOS developer conference 2010 at NYC by HP Palm.  You can get all the presentations that you have missed in the palm of your hands through this app.  

This app is free to get and will always be free.  It is my intent with this to help bring app development awareness to webOS and how easy it really is.

These videos were NOT done by me but by HP Palm.  These videos are sources at the Palm channel on Youtube but I decided to App these into a convenient portal to them.  Permission by Palm was given to make this application.
